3:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18bbe92f4270aee16fdbf6da0c41a8d0fef25d8","tid":1808093,"uid":124382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:17:02.000Z","msg":"啲狗又一見你開始就舉旗、tear gas、腰斬、圍捕。"},{"pid":"ca8133094ca468dac0c527d216bc0abb2fec3c1a","tid":1808093,"uid":50719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:20:11.000Z","msg":"7:00開始，7:15叫你取消，8:00即拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947f47df47c1608f2d3734ebc60aa7f46a06b91f","tid":1808093,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n先支爆，後港獨，才係香港唯一出路<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808018</a>"},{"pid":"69f577e52a82a3febf90d55a8f3e36941562fbe0","tid":1808093,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:26:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edbbbc604f7f818ada9449173a51835fc3d3074b","tid":1808093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c41a4b231894f5a1a59942bc8f0654426e5750","tid":1808093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:17:05.000Z","msg":"【1月3日晚上7-9時 中環愛丁堡廣場】<br />\n教協「無懼白色恐怖 堅守教育專業」教育界集會<br />\n<br />\n集會詳情：<br />\n日期：2020年1月3日<br />\n集會地點：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n集會時間：下午7時至9時<br />\n（已獲警方發出不反對通知書）<br />\n<br />\n過去半年，政府及建制人士連番針對教育界及前線教師作出攻擊，歸咎通識科教育失敗、造謠教師煽動年輕人上街、未審先判被投訴的教師專業失當。近日教育局更把施壓升級，表示將會更嚴厲跟進被捕及被投訴的個案。教育局局長楊潤雄接受內地官媒表示，若學校及校長支持被調查的教師，可取消校長資格。<br />\n<br />\n種種的無理打壓，威嚇教育界，製造白色恐怖，目的在把政治事件諉過於教育界，把教育界當作代罪羔羊，並要令教育界噤聲，做法令人極度憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n因此，教協將於1月3日（星期五晚上7時）舉行教育界「無懼白色恐怖，堅守教育專業」的晚間集會，我們呼籲教育界必須團結一致，放學後與同事和朋友一起出席集會，以最強烈的聲音向教育局和白色恐怖齊聲說不。"},{"pid":"7373f3c0f9d4214f4b9fc328eb1593f66bf8a5d7","tid":1808093,"uid":123988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbe33d1642ec00356e83a5e0275a66b46ca6c86","tid":1808093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"POE RN 19014785<br />\n組織 : 香港教育專業人員協會<br />\n日期 : 2020 年 1 月 3 日(星期五)<br />\n時間 : 晚 上 7 時正 至 晚 上 9 時 正 結 束<br />\n地點 : 中 環 愛 丁 堡 廣 場 大 會 堂 低 座 對 出 空 地<br />\n活動性質 : 公 眾 集 會<br />\n活動目的 : 爭 取 教 師 權 益"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:29:16.000Z","msg":"有無申請埋不反對通知？<br />\n不噴胡椒通知？<br />\n不驅散通知同不拘捕通知？"},{"pid":"ac37d714cb656153b9337e1b9821edd011707922","tid":1808093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3c48b8c197464dc39b95da522e3d127743a3eb","tid":1808093,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17d2cc908b81aa746c8d08858259fdfc7d0489c0","tid":1808093,"uid":110583,"like":0